    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Result: most are not normally distributed (null hypothesis rejected within alpha 0.05)\n",
        "\n",
        "## Mann-Whitney U-test\n",
        "\n",
        "they are not normally distributed, hence we use the U-test to test for difference between means\n",
        "(variances and size of sample do not matter)\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.callout-tip}\n",
        "non significant means normally distributed (or rather can't reject the null hypothesis)\n",
